OL,3,C'It's transformative': Hard-of-hearing
OL,4,Ccinema goers try glasses with subtitles
OL,6,FIt gives people who rely on subtitles
OL,7,Fa far wider choice of films as they
OL,8,Fare not limited to certain showings.
OL,10,FDavid Hedges, who has been deaf since
OL,11,Fhe was a child, now comes to the
OL,12,Fcinema with his son - but often has no
OL,13,Fidea what is happening.
OL,15,F"Especially if it's something
OL,16,Fanimated," he said. "You can't lipread
OL,17,Fa cartoon."
