OL,3,C'It's transformative': Hard-of-hearing
OL,4,Ccinema goers try glasses with subtitles
OL,6,FHe added: "With something like this I
OL,7,Fcan come at 6pm on a Saturday evening,
OL,8,Fwatch a film without it being
OL,9,Frestricted to me anymore, which is
OL,10,Ffantastic."
OL,12,FFiona Blackburn, whose hearing has
OL,13,Fdeteriorated with age, watches films
OL,14,Fwith subtitles at home but struggles
OL,15,Fat the cinema.
OL,17,FShe said: "I come often and not all
OL,18,Fthe films are subtitled. It's totally
OL,19,Ftransformative.
