OL,3,C'It's transformative': Hard-of-hearing
OL,4,Ccinema goers try glasses with subtitles
OL,6,F"You can get totally involved in the
OL,7,Ffilm - it's pure escapism."
OL,9,FThe Alhambra cinema in Keswick,
OL,10,FCumbria, has purchased two pairs of
OL,11,Fthe glasses - at a cost of #5,000 -
OL,12,Fwhich provide an 'on-demand' service
OL,13,Ffor people who need them.
OL,15,FThey were piloted in several UK
OL,16,Fcinemas earlier this year and the
OL,17,FAlhambra is an early adopter of the
OL,18,Ftechnology.
