OL,3,C'It's transformative': Hard-of-hearing
OL,4,Ccinema goers try glasses with subtitles
OL,6,FCarol Rennie, the cinema's co-
OL,7,Fdirector, trialled the headsets a year
OL,8,Fago and described the glasses as
OL,9,F"gamechanging".
OL,11,FShe said: "It shows that we're here
OL,12,Ffor everybody. We're accessible for
OL,13,Feveryone.
OL,15,F"What is means is that people can come
OL,16,Fwho otherwise would not have come. So
OL,17,Fit won't make a huge difference to
OL,18,Faudience numbers but what it means is
OL,19,Fwe won't be excluding people."
