OL,3,C'It's transformative': Hard-of-hearing
OL,4,Ccinema goers try glasses with subtitles
OL,6,FThe money to buy the glasses came from
OL,7,Fthe family of avid cinema goer
OL,8,FGeoffrey Hayes, who died this year.
OL,10,FA keen cinema goer, he enjoyed going
OL,11,Fto the Alhambra and was part of the
OL,12,FKeswick Film Club but found deafness
OL,13,Fin later life increasingly isolating.
OL,15,FChinty Turnbull, his daughter, said:
OL,16,F"Towards the end of his life, he
OL,17,Fwatched films with subtitles. But it
OL,18,Fwas difficult still. So when he passed
OL,19,Faway recently I thought it would be
OL,20,Fnice to do something for him that he
OL,21,Fwould appreciate.
